methodology.source: Reverse-engineered from 3,375 verified pump episodes on Kraken (2024-2026)

components.vol_trend (0-15): 35% of pumps showed rising volume pre-move
components.range_comp (0-15): Volatility compression = coiled spring before breakout
components.obv_accum (0-15): OBV rising while price flat = smart money accumulating
components.vol_spike (0-10): 32% of pumps had 2x+ volume spike at start
components.momentum (0-10): EMA9/21 crossover or approach = momentum shifting
components.consolidation (0-10): Tight sideways action = ready to break out
